QuestData.Title: Work Order: The August Celestials II
QuestData.Description: Once your striped melons are ready to be picked, you'll need only to package them for pick-up.$b$bA trainee from the Cradle of Chi-Ji will be along shortly to collect their order.
QuestData.LogDescription: Harvest 8 Ripe Striped Melon plants and provide 40 Striped Melons for the August Celestials.
